phrases: Both of you, fasten your seat belts.
There will be quite a jolt when we touch down.
Commence landing in a suitable location.
We have landed on Planet Namek!
What kind of place is it?
We cannot see much through this mist.
Are you sure this is it?
Are you trying to put it down!?
We should be able to tell right away by looking at the Dragon Radar.
Good grief, you are so skeptical...
You are finally awake, are you?
The biggest quack doctor on the planet.
He is been bad company for me for 300 years now.
That is how we say hello on this world.
You know, you are lucky that I was the one who discovered you.
If it were not for me taking the proper measures,
all three of you would have croaked.
Come on, now, how long are you going to sleep?
Both of you, hurry and wake up.
Um, this is Planet Namek, right?
We can tell just by looking at your faces.
You look just like Kami- sama.
You look just like Piccolo- san, too.
I sure hope you find them okay- the Dragon Balls.
We know everything there is to know about you.
Well, you are Kami- sama's relatives, after all.
I guess there is no reason why you would not.
We will not stand in your way.
Oh, right, where is our spaceship?
Oh, we put it in the storeroom in back.
It is pretty damaged, but still okay, right?
You really are kind-hearted people for doing all this, are not you?
There are three of them grouped together near here!
Let us hurry and go look for them.
With any luck, we can get three of them today.
That thing will not do you any good.
This area is a dangerous one, and teeming with monsters.
If you go out in that toy-like thing, you will get yourself stomped on easily.
All right, what choice do I have but to let you use my goku?
My dear little goku is pretty fast, huh?
With a spaceship like this one...
It has to be around here.
Sorry to have to make you do this, as well.
That is okay, this is staving off boredom.
After all, right now, Earth could be facing a great crisis at any moment, and...
Oh, you know all about it, huh?
It is definitely down there somewhere, no doubt about it.
We could not hold our breaths any longer.
This is going to be really hard.
Still, there is no mistake that it is around here someplace.
Why, when my battle power is far and away higher than his,
did I take that attack dead-on?
What did you do that for out of nowhere!?
Patients should act like patients, and lie there quietly, you know!
I am just so bored, so bored!
I cannot wait to go cut loose!
Patients should not be talkin' nonsense.
Goku- sa, until your body is doing better, you are to behave yourself.
If you can put it on, you can wear it.
These ancient ruins are from four or five-thousand years ago.
Look here, the Dragon Ball is within a 5-meter radius of us.
The Radar's readings are getting stronger.
Their faces are completely different from the way they look now, are not they?
I wonder if there is treasure in them.
Okay, let us find one more before the day is over!
You are sure a chipper old man, huh?
He is a nice fellow, is not he?
Doing this for complete strangers like us.
That is what is so fishy about it.
It is possible that once we get all seven together,
he might be planning to swipe them from us.
Could you set us down soon?
I am fine, but the Radar-
C- could you hand that over?
Telling him that is not going to get through to him!
Y- you cannot go any farther!
We have to hurry, or he will get away, you know!
If you go any farther, your life will be in danger.
Listen, you are not planning to swipe the Dragon Balls from us, are you!?
I- I would not do that.
You are being far too nice to perfect strangers like us.
Let us go have a look.
I am sure it was around here...
That is that thing from earlier!
The water in these swamps is dreadful stuff that will dissolve any living thing,
and the gasses that rise from it will take out any ordinary person who breathes them.
So that is why you stopped us, huh?
I am sorry for saying something so terrible.
Just so long as you know, it is all right.
Still, we are in a jam.
If he is ended up like that, that means the Dragon Ball is in the swamp, right?
How are we going to get it out of there?
Well, I do have a bodysuit for that sort of thing, but even if you
were to wear it to dive down there, it would only be good for ten seconds.
Any longer than that, and the suit will dissolve.
After all, we cannot do anything unless we have that Dragon Ball, right?
I just need to come back up within ten seconds, right?
I will give it a try.
What if we tied a special rope around his body,
to pull him up before ten seconds is up?
All right, let us give it a try.
Judging from the readings on the Radar, it is right underneath us.
We will pull you up with the rope after seven seconds, okay?
The swamp water is stronger than I figured...
Now to hurry up on the rope.
l have to act fast, or I will not make it!
I will not last until l make it to the top like this!
Bulma and the others were ecstatic over already obtaining three of the Balls.
Now then, will they be able to get all of the Dragon Balls without any trouble?
